{"tid":222481,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[曼聯] 摩佬:我已準備踢中堅","createTime":"2017-04-29T14:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T14:49:07.000Z","uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed4c3e12a078b882243ed41dd9145e9ffdc3a06","tid":222481,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:28:27.000Z","msg":"2017年4月29日 上午07:45:02<br />\n曼聯領隊摩連奴表示，中場保羅普巴在周日英超對史雲斯一仗繼續因傷缺陣，並戲言面對陣中傷兵滿營問題，自己已準備就緒可充當中堅一職。<br />\n<br />\n摩帥說︰「普巴可在對切爾達一仗復出，不幸地他是與華倫西亞一樣的輕微拉傷，是因為比賽頻密的正常受傷。」對於球隊的中堅荒問題，他打趣說︰「現在我們只有歷拜利、戴利白蘭特及杜安沙比3個選擇，上仗對曼城拜利和白蘭特踼得很好，<span style=\"color: red;\">我亦已在健身室加緊操練，可與杜安沙比成另一選擇。</span>」"},{"pid":"dd2cd723093194e987feb659b2dec88bd550a292","tid":222481,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3e8cb81efadb28933889fc24780480c6d4a6d4","tid":222481,"uid":11314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:38:12.000Z","msg":"魔性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce97f607f499cb7ac58960f0c277bc1b461c21bb","tid":222481,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魔性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c78c241e1a511d430a8c368de3eb55ab865ffad","tid":222481,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:49:07.000Z","msg":"屌你連杜仔個位都比佢搶撚埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}